item.description:
As the polls close, come celebrate all our hard work at the Courtyard in Concord. Dr Paul will be there! Get out the word to everyone. The band, Naked Blue will be playing.

If you live on the Seacoast, and Concord is too far to drive, or you want to head down there after hanging out in Concord for a while, there will also be a house party in Rye with some of the Operation Live Free or Die Folks with the band that play the "Hope Anthem", starting at 11 pm. More details to follow.
item.name: Celebration
